    Represents a deal taking place at a Market.
    Entity
    Base class for all managed objects in package.
    Food
    Represents a food item.
    FoodProperty
    Represents a property of a Food.
    Market
    Represents a physical location selling Foods.
    PasswordResetToken

    Represents a recipe for a culinary dish.
    Review

    ReviewProperty

    Role
    An authority granted to Users to determine privileges.
    Tag

    Tip
    Represents a tip of one of various types.
    UGC
    Represents User generated content.
    User
    Represents a user of the system.
    Viewing

    ViewingPk
    Primary key of a Viewing.
